reviews.text: Woman on the gate is always nasty and making rude comments. Also toilets are never open. Other than that it would be a good station
Had the misfortune to use the disgusting toilet. Looks like it hasn't been cleaned properly for a long time.

My daughter payed for ticket on line and when she went to pick it up machine not working then to top it off went for help and got told had to buy another even though she all ready payed for one ...she ended up missing her train as they gave her the run around and ended up train leaving befor she had chance to board seriously nit happy with service given staff need a shake up and retraining in customer care
We aren't in Fareham all that often. We find this station nice and clean and tidy. Not had much dealings with the staff,any we have were helpful and friendly enough.

Apauling servise, I had left my wallet at home so used the train line app to purchase a ticket using Apple Pay, I wasn’t able to get my actually tickets from the machine without my card and I wasn’t aloud through to the platform even after showing my ticket on the App, ticket master told me I either get my card or he can’t help me!
